Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.38,0:00:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我好好說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請成為蒔菜的爸爸吧
